I've just been thinking a lot lately.......
I'm usually not the type to really care what others think of me, but for some reason I do....
I always try to be what everyone else wants me to be and I don't know who I am......
I try my best to get everything done to the best of my ability in a timely manner, but it doesn't feel like I do it right or fast enough...... I find myself questioning why I am here and what am I trying to do with my life..... I still don't know what I want to do with my life..... I'm only 19 and feel so confused about things..... There are only a few things that I am sure of right now.......
I know I want to finish college..... I know I want to be in Michigan with Katina........ I know I love Katina with all my heart...... I know I need to work really hard and pay off everything......
I'm just not really sure after that other than my basic needs..... (ie: food, air, water, cloths, etc.)....... 

Now, after reading all that..... If you are my friend, or somewhat know me, I want you to leave me a comment to tell me what you think about me. 

What kind of person do you feel I am?
Do you like me?
What is it about me that you bother?
Am I a burden to you sometimes?
Do I make you mad often?
How would you rate me on a scale of 1-10? (character wise)
How long have you known me?
How close do you feel we are?
Do you think i'm fat?
What do you think I can do to better myself? 
Do you think I'm depressed? If so, why?
What would you do if I were there with you right now?
How did we meet?
Do you remember our first conversation?
Do I make you happy?
How often do we talk?
Am I annoying?
Should I keep shaved, tamed, or scruffy? (my face)
How do you like my hair?
What is one thing you would change on me? (you can list more than one if you'ld like)
Where do you feel my life is going?
Do you think i'm doing the right things?
Are you tired of my questions?

I'll stop there........ I'm sure I could come up with more things to ask, but I need to get back to studying for my test.......

I love you Katina and I'm sorry about this morning....... I wish we could talk about things though instead of you hanging up on me..... I'm not saying that to pick on you or be mean, but I really prefer talking out things instead of avoiding them........ *kiss* I love you with all my heart.... Please don't forget that......

And thank you to the rest of you who fill out my questions... It means a lot to me......

~Aaron~

Dumb phone......... 9. Flight plans being changed...... 10. Almost failing a class......... 11. Missing school for the first time in more than 6 months of going straight...... 12. Failing a driving test......... 13. Going to the movies......... 14. Playing putt putt golf.......... 15. Went swimming for the first time in months....... 16. Shopping......... I'm sure there is more, but that kinda covers what I can remember at the moment..... If anything I still have to go to the store today to buy some batteries for my broken fire alarm and I need to go to the cell phone shop to buy a charger for my phone so I can have one at work...... It's going to be a real hectic schedule for me for the next few weeks, but I'll live........ I just have to finish packing for my new apartment, clean up my old apartment, take my driving test, go to the post office, get all my class work done, time the bus schedule, meet up with the people who will be handling my electricity, talk to the owners of where I work to see if I can get a promotion, and many other things.......
